		Bezi: Yeah I don’t know how I managed myself. How’d the mission go?
		update Katerina [extra_data="set Mood/Smug"]
		Katerina: Success! Though Zdzichu zranění…
		Bezi: Huh? What does that mean?
		update Katerina [extra_data="set Mood/Base"]
		Katerina: Uhh… he not good.
		Bezi: What? He’s injured? Don’t tell me we got shot?!
		update Katerina [extra_data="set Mood/Smug"]
		No no! Idiot just fall from ladder. Had to carry him back. Alina léčit him now. You did good.
