		Hippie: Yeah… we definitely WEREN'T betting on whether you'll return…
		join Katerina center [extra_data="set Mood/Smug"]
		Katerina: Pay up…
		Hippie: Shh… not now.
		Bezi: ...
		Bezi: So? Did it work?
		update Danuta [extra_data="set Mood/Happy"]
